  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. The computational model predicts absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed across all 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors. Seven factors were formally assessed; six factors were scoped out due to epistemic gaps at MRL 5. All assessed factors achieved required gradation levels under the Minimal conformance profile. Decision: Accepted. Note: this package conforms to ProfileMinimal; structured hasContextOfUse is not mandated by this profile and is therefore omitted — intended-use scope is described in the bound Requirement and Claim prose only.",
